name: Space Style TI
description:
Genral Info

Space Stlye was another of my first embeddings I made back in 2022. It is still useable on newer models. It adds a space theme to the enviroment and the character itself. Like pastel_style it main use is for Portraits. So, for best use, I would use it with any kind of portrait type image.

Added Example Images with simple prompt from:

  • Kenshi

  • AbyssOrangeMix_nsfw/hard

Usage

To use this embedding you have to download the file aswell as drop it into the "\stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings" folder

To use it in a prompt: "space_style"

For some models it can be to strong, so use this instead

"(space_style:0.8)"

Have fun :)
